Simple tool to display LOC (lines of code) history for git current branch.

Example:

2010-05-12 14:40:54     1074    +2    -1     dict kick
2010-05-12 14:52:03     1074    +5    -5     minor cosmetic
2010-05-13 12:52:57     1085   +24   -13     atoms from forth
2010-05-13 12:56:10     1095   +14    -4     display
2010-05-13 13:07:46     1096    +4    -3     display tuneup


